{"tid":1246710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每朝搭巴士見到塊玻璃都好撚想嘔","createTime":"2019-06-21T00:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T23:58:35.000Z","uid":32435,"like":113,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"39db91d69a3fe0557b9bf1e84bbf3ffae4f3b6af","tid":1246710,"uid":32435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:01:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，訓撚到個頭貼撚實塊玻璃<br />\n<br />\n玻璃上面個浸閪邊油，多到可以炸到薯條<br />\n<br />\n坐係個位望出街，就好似800度近視咁<br />\n<br />\n乜撚都Blur 鳩哂<br />\n<br />\n你班毒撚係巴士訓個時可唔可比D 公德<br />\n<br />\n跟據經驗，呢個情況係狗巴出現比較多<br />\n<br />\n新巴城巴會好小小<br />\n<br />\n究竟個塊閪玻璃幾耐清潔一次？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得男人到左三十歲仲要依賴交通工具好可憐<br />\n<br />\n當可憐下我啦"},{"pid":"e3daa742e6f1649e68841b201383cb2190bf930e","tid":1246710,"uid":84128,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"你識舞空術？"},{"pid":"f31fb1c92a72a5809aa6490ad47482a5da49edc5","tid":1246710,"uid":56148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:07:58.000Z","msg":"有次頂唔順 用濕紙巾抹左d油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981436e4e546841e378f1398f3f54173d87e215d","tid":1246710,"uid":32435,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e3daa742e6f1649e68841b201383cb2190bf930e","tid":1246710,"uid":84128,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"你識舞空術？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3orif7N2qBUUJ2hUK4/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3orif7N2qBUUJ2hUK4%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e525937c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e12e4ce206f27ce44d6ea03ad4fa9a357f29980b","tid":1246710,"uid":32435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f31fb1c92a72a5809aa6490ad47482a5da49edc5","tid":1246710,"uid":56148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:07:58.000Z","msg":"有次頂唔